<?xml version="1.0"?>
<?mso-application progid="Excel.Sheet"?>
<Workbook xmlns="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:spreadsheet"
 xmlns:o="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office"
 xmlns:x="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:excel"
 xmlns:ss="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:spreadsheet"
 xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40">

<Styles>
  <Style ss:ID="Default" ss:Name="Normal">
    <Alignment ss:Vertical="Top" ss:WrapText="1"/>
    <Borders/>
    <Font ss:FontName="Calibri" ss:Size="11" ss:Color="#1F2937"/>
    <Interior/>
    <NumberFormat/>
    <Protection/>
  </Style>
  <Style ss:ID="Header">
    <Alignment ss:Vertical="Top" ss:WrapText="1"/>
    <Font ss:FontName="Calibri" ss:Size="11" ss:Bold="1" ss:Color="#FFFFFF"/>
    <Interior ss:Color="#1F3A5F" ss:Pattern="Solid"/>
  </Style>
  <Style ss:ID="Title">
    <Alignment ss:Vertical="Top" ss:WrapText="1"/>
    <Font ss:FontName="Calibri" ss:Size="12" ss:Bold="1" ss:Color="#132033"/>
    <Interior ss:Color="#EAF2F1" ss:Pattern="Solid"/>
  </Style>
  <Style ss:ID="Wrap"/>
  <Style ss:ID="Critical">
    <Alignment ss:Vertical="Top" ss:WrapText="1"/>
    <Font ss:FontName="Calibri" ss:Size="11" ss:Color="#7F1D1D"/>
    <Interior ss:Color="#FDECEC" ss:Pattern="Solid"/>
  </Style>
</Styles>

<Worksheet ss:Name="Runbook"><Table><Column ss:AutoFitWidth="0" ss:Width="130"/><Column ss:AutoFitWidth="0" ss:Width="520"/><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Header"><Data ss:Type="String">Field</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Header"><Data ss:Type="String">Value</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Plan title</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Suite language rewrite plan, logged-in UI only</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Date</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">2026-04-28</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Register</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Product</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Owner</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Codex autonomous rewrite pass</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Objective</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Rewrite the logged-in suite copy from internal Verisight model language to calm, practical Dutch that is immediately clear for HR and manager users.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Primary personas</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">1. HR owner or HR member who needs quick orientation, campaign progress, reports and follow-up.&#10;2. Manager assignee who only works in Action Center and should not be taught internal architecture.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">In scope</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Login helper copy, activation helper copy, shell labels, access denied states, overview home, reports home, campaign detail, Action Center landing and Action Center subviews.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Out of scope</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Public website, billing, proof, telemetry, access logic, roles model, admin-only beheer routes unless a user-facing suite label depends on them.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Do not change</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Product structure, navigation truth, Action Center top-level position, data logic, gating logic, report availability logic, campaign state logic.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Rewrite principles</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">1. Prefer user task language over Verisight system language.&#10;2. Explain what the user can do now, not how the platform is internally composed.&#10;3. Use plain Dutch by default. Keep product names only where they are true product names.&#10;4. Remove architecture words like suite-shell, bronlaag, bounded, productwaarheid unless they are absolutely necessary.&#10;5. Replace managementread and management-ready with everyday terms like overzicht, samenvatting, klaar voor bespreking.&#10;6. Managers should hear what they can access, not why internal insights layers exist.&#10;7. Keep tone calm, exact and premium. No hype, no inside baseball.&#10;8. Keep copy shorter where it currently over-explains philosophy.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Execution order</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">1. Shell and global labels&#10;2. Login and activation helper text&#10;3. Access denied and manager-only copy&#10;4. Overview&#10;5. Reports&#10;6. Campaign detail&#10;7. Action Center landing&#10;8. Action Center subviews&#10;9. QA and parity pass</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Acceptance criteria</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">A. HR can scan home and understand what is open, what is next and where to go.&#10;B. Manager can land in Action Center without being told about internal platform layers.&#10;C. Shell language is consistent, preferably Dutch-first with stable product names.&#10;D. No misleading route names for manager-only users.&#10;E. No product logic regressions.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Existing QA assets</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Desktop and mobile suite screenshots already exist in frontend/.tmp-visual-qa/2026-04-27-autonomous-pass.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Wake instruction</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">When resuming, read this workbook first, then execute the queue top to bottom. Do not reopen the audit unless a copy conflict appears after edits.</Data></Cell></Row></Table></Worksheet><Worksheet ss:Name="Execution Queue"><Table><Column ss:AutoFitWidth="0" ss:Width="45"/><Column ss:AutoFitWidth="0" ss:Width="70"/><Column ss:AutoFitWidth="0" ss:Width="120"/><Column ss:AutoFitWidth="0" ss:Width="110"/><Column ss:AutoFitWidth="0" ss:Width="220"/><Column ss:AutoFitWidth="0" ss:Width="220"/><Column ss:AutoFitWidth="0" ss:Width="250"/><Column ss:AutoFitWidth="0" ss:Width="220"/><Column ss:AutoFitWidth="0" ss:Width="170"/><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Header"><Data ss:Type="String">Order</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Header"><Data ss:Type="String">Status</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Header"><Data ss:Type="String">Surface</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Header"><Data ss:Type="String">Primary persona</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Header"><Data ss:Type="String">Goal</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Header"><Data ss:Type="String">Files</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Header"><Data ss:Type="String">Rewrite focus</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Header"><Data ss:Type="String">Done when</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Header"><Data ss:Type="String">Verification</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">planned</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Shell and global labels</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">HR + manager</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Make the environment feel like one product in one language, without mixed English or architecture jargon.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/lib/dashboard/shell-navigation.ts&#10;frontend/components/dashboard/dashboard-shell.tsx</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Overview to Overzicht, Reports to Rapporten, review manager-only footer text, remove suite-shell phrasing, fix manager back link naming.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Primary nav, footer and current labels read naturally in Dutch and match actual access paths.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Lint touched files, screenshot shell on HR and manager variants.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">planned</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Login and activation helper copy</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">HR + manager</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Explain access simply and practically before login or account completion.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/app/(auth)/login/page.tsx&#10;frontend/app/(auth)/complete-account/page.tsx</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Replace follow-through, first read, handoff and self-service framing with simpler account readiness wording.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">A user can tell in one read whether they will enter dashboard or Action Center and what needs to be ready first.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Visual spot check login and complete-account pages.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">planned</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Access denied and manager-only states</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Manager</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Make restrictions feel helpful and clear, not technical.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/components/dashboard/suite-access-denied.tsx&#10;frontend/app/(dashboard)/reports/page.tsx&#10;frontend/app/(dashboard)/campaigns/[id]/page.tsx</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Replace manager-only scope, same suite-login, follow-through layer and campaignreads with direct access language.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Denied pages answer three things fast: where you are, what you cannot open, where you should go instead.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Route tests plus screenshots for denied reports and denied campaign detail.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">4</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">planned</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Overview home</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">HR</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Turn home into a clear operating overview, not a lesson in internal product logic.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/app/(dashboard)/dashboard/page.tsx</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Remove suite-shell, managementread, management-ready, bounded, managementduiding and first read where they are not essential. Keep product truth and campaign truth.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Hero, summary notes, focus rail and portfolio labels all read as practical status and next step language.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Run dashboard tests, lint page, compare desktop screenshot before and after.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">5</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">planned</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Reports home</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">HR</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Make reports feel like usable discussion output, not internal handoff theory.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/app/(dashboard)/reports/page.tsx</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Replace managementread, handofflaag, MT-ready handoff, bounded handoff with discussion-ready, samenvatting, vervolgafspraak and owner-next-step language.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Reports page still conveys the sequence dashboard to report to action center, but in plain Dutch.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Run reports shell test, lint page, screenshot reports desktop.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">6</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">planned</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Campaign detail</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">HR</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Keep the detail route strong and premium, but remove copy that explains the Verisight framework instead of the situation.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/app/(dashboard)/campaigns/[id]/page.tsx</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Rewrite hero intro, summary layer labels, follow-on suggestions, route labels and operational helper text. Keep true product names where needed. Avoid bounded portfolio, managementread and architecture phrasing.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">A first-time HR user understands the campaign state and next move without knowing Verisight internal language.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Run campaign detail tests, lint page, screenshot campaign detail desktop.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">7</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">planned</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Action Center landing</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">HR + manager</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Keep the module strong, but remove platform philosophy from the first read.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/app/(dashboard)/action-center/page.tsx&#10;frontend/components/dashboard/action-center-preview.tsx</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Replace suite-shell, bronlaag, bounded, productwaarheid, cockpit and consumerflow phrasing with direct operational language.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Landing tells users what needs attention, who owns it and when it returns, without architecture words.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Run action-center shell test, lint files, screenshots for HR and manager landing.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">8</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">planned</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Action Center subviews</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">HR + manager</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Make actions, reviews, managers and teams read like working views, not like design doctrine.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/components/dashboard/action-center-preview.tsx</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Rewrite ownershipmodel, bounded adminroute, bronlaag los trekken, read-only vanuit de bronlaag, bounded adminlaag and similar phrases. Keep manager assignment truth intact.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Subview labels and helper text sound task-based and concrete.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Spot check all subviews, especially managers and create-action modal.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">9</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">planned</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">QA and parity pass</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">HR + manager</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Catch drift and ensure the new language stays consistent end to end.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">All touched user-facing suite files</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Unify repeated labels, remove leftovers, keep Dutch-first wording and preserve product names consistently.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">No visible jargon leftovers on key screens, no mixed navigation language, no misleading manager routes.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Run focused tests, eslint, authenticated screenshot sweep for HR and manager.</Data></Cell></Row></Table></Worksheet><Worksheet ss:Name="Rewrite Inventory"><Table><Column ss:AutoFitWidth="0" ss:Width="55"/><Column ss:AutoFitWidth="0" ss:Width="120"/><Column ss:AutoFitWidth="0" ss:Width="90"/><Column ss:AutoFitWidth="0" ss:Width="65"/><Column ss:AutoFitWidth="0" ss:Width="210"/><Column ss:AutoFitWidth="0" ss:Width="200"/><Column ss:AutoFitWidth="0" ss:Width="210"/><Column ss:AutoFitWidth="0" ss:Width="230"/><Column ss:AutoFitWidth="0" ss:Width="70"/><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Header"><Data ss:Type="String">ID</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Header"><Data ss:Type="String">Surface</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Header"><Data ss:Type="String">Persona</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Header"><Data ss:Type="String">Severity</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Header"><Data ss:Type="String">Current copy or term</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Header"><Data ss:Type="String">Problem</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Header"><Data ss:Type="String">Rewrite direction</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Header"><Data ss:Type="String">File</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Header"><Data ss:Type="String">Line</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">L-01</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Login</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Manager</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Critical"><Data ss:Type="String">high</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">follow-through werkruimte</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Internal concept language, not user language.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Use Action Center as the concrete destination name.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/app/(auth)/login/page.tsx</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">111</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">L-02</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Login</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">HR</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">medium</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">eerste read</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Still sounds like product doctrine.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Use eerste overzicht or eerste gesprek only if needed.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/app/(auth)/login/page.tsx</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">108-114</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">A-01</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Complete account</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">HR</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">medium</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">handoff-moment</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Explains internal delivery framing instead of user readiness.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Describe that the account opens when dashboard and respondents are ready for the user.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/app/(auth)/complete-account/page.tsx</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">178-179</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">S-01</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Shell nav</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">HR + manager</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Critical"><Data ss:Type="String">high</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Overview</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Mixed language on primary navigation.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Rename to Overzicht.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/lib/dashboard/shell-navigation.ts</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">44</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">S-02</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Shell nav</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">HR + manager</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Critical"><Data ss:Type="String">high</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Reports</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Mixed language on primary navigation.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Rename to Rapporten.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/lib/dashboard/shell-navigation.ts</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">50</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">S-03</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Shell footer</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Manager</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">medium</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">manager-only workspace binnen dezelfde suite-shell</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Architecture and English drift in footer.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Use practical footer copy such as Action Center voor managers.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/components/dashboard/dashboard-shell.tsx</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">236-238</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">S-04</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Manager shell</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Manager</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Critical"><Data ss:Type="String">high</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Terug naar dashboard</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Misleading route hint for manager-only access.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Rename to Terug naar Action Center-overzicht or remove.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/components/dashboard/dashboard-shell.tsx</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">269-274</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">D-01</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Access denied</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Manager</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Critical"><Data ss:Type="String">high</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Manager-only scope</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">English plus internal access label.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Use Alleen Action Center or Alleen managerwerkruimte.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/components/dashboard/suite-access-denied.tsx</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">23</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">D-02</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Access denied</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Manager</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Critical"><Data ss:Type="String">high</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">follow-through laag</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Internal architecture phrase.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Explain simply that managers do not see reports or campaign insights.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/components/dashboard/suite-access-denied.tsx</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">39-40</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">O-01</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Overview hero</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">HR</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Critical"><Data ss:Type="String">high</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">suite-shell</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Architecture leak in hero supporting copy.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Remove entirely or replace with deze omgeving.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/app/(dashboard)/dashboard/page.tsx</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">244</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">O-02</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Overview hero</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">HR</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Critical"><Data ss:Type="String">high</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">managementread</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Too internal for home orientation.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Use eerste overzicht or genoeg informatie voor gesprek.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/app/(dashboard)/dashboard/page.tsx</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">252</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">O-03</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Overview summary</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">HR</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Critical"><Data ss:Type="String">high</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">management-ready</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Jargon on key summary note.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Use klaar voor bespreking.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/app/(dashboard)/dashboard/page.tsx</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">259</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">O-04</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Overview lead route</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">HR</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Critical"><Data ss:Type="String">high</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">bounded suite-taal</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Pure internal doctrine language.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Explain the route in user outcome terms only.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/app/(dashboard)/dashboard/page.tsx</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">373</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">O-05</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Overview focus rail</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">HR</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">medium</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Context blijft bounded en rustig</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Reads like design principle, not operational value.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Rewrite as concrete portfolio guidance.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/app/(dashboard)/dashboard/page.tsx</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">652-653</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">R-01</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Reports hero</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">HR</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Critical"><Data ss:Type="String">high</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">managementread en handofflaag</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Too many internal labels in the primary explanation.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Use samenvatting voor overleg and wat daarna wordt opgepakt.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/app/(dashboard)/reports/page.tsx</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">105</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">R-02</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Reports meta chip</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">HR</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">medium</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">MT-ready handoff</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Internal phrase and English hybrid.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Use klaar voor MT-bespreking or klaar voor overleg.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/app/(dashboard)/reports/page.tsx</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">125-126</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">R-03</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Reports library intro</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">HR</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Critical"><Data ss:Type="String">high</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Rapporten met echte managementread</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Jargon in section title.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Use Rapporten die klaar zijn voor bespreking.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/app/(dashboard)/reports/page.tsx</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">202-203</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">R-04</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Reports helper text</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">HR</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Critical"><Data ss:Type="String">high</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">bounded handoff</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Architecture-heavy phrase.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Use overdracht naar opvolging or vervolgafspraak.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/app/(dashboard)/reports/page.tsx</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">193, 295, 318-329</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">C-01</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Campaign detail hero</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">HR</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Critical"><Data ss:Type="String">high</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Campaign detail bundelt managementread</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Internal framing at top of page.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Rewrite as what this campaign now shows plus what is next.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/app/(dashboard)/campaigns/[id]/page.tsx</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">1702-1705</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">C-02</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Campaign labels</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">HR</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">medium</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Bestuurlijke handoff</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Potentially understandable but repeated too often and sounds process-heavy.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Use compacte samenvatting or eerste duiding where possible.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/app/(dashboard)/campaigns/[id]/page.tsx</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">2019, 2097</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">C-03</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Campaign follow-on helper</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">HR</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Critical"><Data ss:Type="String">high</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">bounded, automatisch groter productverhaal</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Internal ideology instead of practical caution.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Explain simply when a next route is helpful and when not.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/app/(dashboard)/campaigns/[id]/page.tsx</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">2475-2481</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">C-04</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Campaign execution helper</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">HR</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">medium</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">deliveryrecords blijven bewust bij Verisight</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Leaks backend object naming.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Use uitvoercontrole or campagne-uitvoering.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/app/(dashboard)/campaigns/[id]/page.tsx</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">2542</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">C-05</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Campaign deny state</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Manager</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Critical"><Data ss:Type="String">high</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Campaigninzichten blijven buiten je manager-scope</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Internal access framing.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Use je ziet hier geen campaigndetails with a clear redirect to Action Center.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/app/(dashboard)/campaigns/[id]/page.tsx</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">227-228</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">AC-01</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Action Center subtitle</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">HR + manager</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Critical"><Data ss:Type="String">high</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">zelfde suite-shell</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Architecture phrase in first read.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Use deze omgeving or omit.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/app/(dashboard)/action-center/page.tsx</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">266-267</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">AC-02</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Action Center empty state</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">HR + manager</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Critical"><Data ss:Type="String">high</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">bounded deliverycontext, follow-through dossiers</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Very internal explanation in empty state.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Explain what kinds of open actions make this module appear.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/app/(dashboard)/action-center/page.tsx</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">279-280</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">AC-03</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Action Center empty state</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">HR + manager</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Critical"><Data ss:Type="String">high</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">bronlaag, losse cockpit, suite-shell</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Platform philosophy instead of user help.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Describe source campaigns and follow-up plainly.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/app/(dashboard)/action-center/page.tsx</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">288-289</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">AC-04</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Action Center overview</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">HR + manager</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Critical"><Data ss:Type="String">high</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">eerste managementread</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Still too framework-like for the main explanation.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Use eerste overzicht van wat nu besproken moet worden.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/components/dashboard/action-center-preview.tsx</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">251-252, 783</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">AC-05</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Action Center managers</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">HR + manager</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Critical"><Data ss:Type="String">high</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Ownershipmodel</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">English-model label in a Dutch working view.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Use Eigenaarschap or Managers per team.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/components/dashboard/action-center-preview.tsx</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">1389-1393</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">AC-06</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Action Center managers</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">HR + manager</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Critical"><Data ss:Type="String">high</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">bounded suite-shell, bronlaag los te trekken</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Meta architecture language in manager assignment copy.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Rewrite to concrete assignment language only.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/components/dashboard/action-center-preview.tsx</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">1393, 1423-1426</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">AC-07</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Action Center create action</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">HR + manager</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">medium</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">bounded adminlaag</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Internal phrase in modal helper text.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Use in Action Center or in deze opvolgingslijst.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/components/dashboard/action-center-preview.tsx</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">1672</Data></Cell></Row></Table></Worksheet><Worksheet ss:Name="Replacement Dictionary"><Table><Column ss:AutoFitWidth="0" ss:Width="120"/><Column ss:AutoFitWidth="0" ss:Width="130"/><Column ss:AutoFitWidth="0" ss:Width="220"/><Column ss:AutoFitWidth="0" ss:Width="220"/><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Header"><Data ss:Type="String">Internal or weak term</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Header"><Data ss:Type="String">Default replacement</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Header"><Data ss:Type="String">Use notes</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Header"><Data ss:Type="String">Keep only when</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">suite-shell</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">deze omgeving</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Usually remove completely.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Only if technical shell distinction is truly necessary in admin documentation.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">managementread</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">eerste overzicht</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Sometimes samenvatting for overleg is even better.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Only if tied to a true product term, which is currently not necessary on user-facing screens.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">management-ready</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">klaar voor bespreking</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Short, practical, outcome-based.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Do not keep in chips or hero copy.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">managementduiding</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">duiding</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Or wat dit nu betekent.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Keep only sparingly in reports if really needed.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">bounded</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">remove</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">If caution is needed, explain the limit directly.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Only in deep admin or technical copy.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">bronlaag</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">onderliggende campagne</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Or oorspronkelijke campagne.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Never on first-read copy for manager or HR.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">productwaarheid</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">bron blijft leidend</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Often removable.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Only in admin documentation.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">follow-through</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">opvolging</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Much clearer in Dutch.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">No reason to keep English term.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">handoff</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">overdracht</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Often better as na dit rapport or vervolgstap.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Keep only if discussing true transfer moment in admin context.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">cadens</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">ritme</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Or terugkommoment.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Do not use cadens on user-facing home screens.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">workbench</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">bronoverzicht</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Or dossierbron if admin-only.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Never for HR or manager-facing primary copy.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">manager-only scope</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">alleen Action Center</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Plain access language.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Do not keep mixed English labels.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">campaignread or campaignreads</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">campagnedetail of campagneoverzicht</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Prefer existing route truth.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">No need for read wording.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">owner</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">eigenaar of verantwoordelijke</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Choose whichever is more natural per sentence.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Keep owner only in code, not copy.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">cockpit</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">remove</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Sounds like strategy deck language.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Never needed here.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">consumerflows or carriers</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">remove</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Pure internal jargon.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Never needed here.</Data></Cell></Row></Table></Worksheet><Worksheet ss:Name="Wake Packet"><Table><Column ss:AutoFitWidth="0" ss:Width="140"/><Column ss:AutoFitWidth="0" ss:Width="560"/><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Header"><Data ss:Type="String">Field</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Header"><Data ss:Type="String">Value</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Resume contract</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Use this workbook as the execution brief. Do not reopen the audit unless copy changed elsewhere. Edit only logged-in suite UI copy. Preserve route truth and product logic.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Suggested implementation order</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Shell labels first, then login and denied states, then overview, reports, campaign detail, Action Center landing, Action Center subviews, then QA.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Edit constraints</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Do not change billing, proof, telemetry, public website, access logic or product structure. Action Center stays top-level. No rollback of product logic.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Priority rule</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Whenever a sentence teaches internal architecture instead of helping the user act, rewrite it.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Manager rule</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Manager copy must answer: what can I do here, what can I not open, where do I go next. Nothing more.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">HR rule</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">HR copy must answer: what is open, what needs attention, what is the next sensible route.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Primary verification commands</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">1. npm test -- "app/(dashboard)/campaigns/[id]/page.test.ts" "app/(dashboard)/dashboard/page.test.ts" "app/(dashboard)/reports/page.route-shell.test.ts" "app/(dashboard)/action-center/page.route-shell.test.ts"&#10;2. npx eslint on all touched suite files&#10;3. Authenticated screenshot sweep using existing .env.local and tests/e2e/.action-center-pilot.json</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Existing authenticated QA assets</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">frontend/.tmp-visual-qa/2026-04-27-autonomous-pass contains HR desktop and mobile screenshots.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Manager QA note</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">After rewrite, capture manager Action Center and denied dashboard or reports state again to confirm navigation and explanation are practical.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Definition of done</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">No high-priority jargon remains on login, shell, deny states, overview, reports, campaign detail and Action Center. HR and manager variants both read as practical product UI, not internal doctrine.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Wake prompt</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Resume by executing the queue in this workbook. Start with shell labels and denied states, then move through the suite surfaces in order. Keep all rewrites Dutch-first, user-facing and action-oriented.</Data></Cell></Row></Table></Worksheet>
</Workbook>
